name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
December 25, Linyi, Shandong. Baiyi Finance raised funds with high interest rates and then collapsed. Victims marched to defend their rights.
December 25, Harbin. Junhao Apartment was left unfinished, and the owners defended their rights.
December 25, Xiamen, Fujian. COFCO Joy City's property quality was poor, the developer reduced the configuration, and the owners defended their rights.
